{"type":"message","id":"b58db46c","parentId":"db456d18","timestamp":"2026-03-23T12:17:44.797Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"搜索失败了，但我可以根据已有知识来回答。用户提到的 minimax/MiniMax-M2.7 可能是指 MiniMax 的新版本模型。M2.1 是之前文档中提到的版本，M2.7 可能是一个更新的版本。\n\n我应该告诉用户如何在配置中添加和使用这个模型。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"你是指 **MiniMax M2.7** 模型吗？如果是，配置方式与 M2.1 类似。\n\n## 配置 MiniMax M2.7\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"env\": {\n    \"KIMI_API_KEY\": \"sk-kimi-...\",\n    \"MINIMAX_API_KEY\": \"sk-minimax-...\"\n  },\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"model\": {\n        \"primary\": \"minimax/MiniMax-M2.7\",     // ← 使用 M2.7\n        \"fallbacks\": [\"kimi-coding/k2p5\"]\n      },\n      \"models\": {\n        \"kimi-coding/k2p5\": { \"alias\": \"Kimi K2.5\" },\n        \"minimax/MiniMax-M2.7\": { \"alias\": \"MiniMax M2.7\" }\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"models\": {\n    \"mode\": \"merge\",\n    \"providers\": {\n      \"minimax\": {\n        \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.minimax.io/anthropic\",\n        \"apiKey\": \"${MINIMAX_API_KEY}\",\n        \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",              // ← 模型 ID\n            \"name\": \"MiniMax M2.7\",\n            \"contextWindow\": 200000,\n            \"maxTokens\": 8192\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 快速切换命令\n\n```bash\n# 临时切换（当前会话）\n/model minimax/MiniMax-M2.7\n\n# 永久修改默认模型\nopenclaw config set agents.defaults.model.primary \"minimax/MiniMax-M2.7\"\n```\n\n需要我帮你更新配置文件吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":239,"output":452,"cacheRead":42496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43187,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774268254210}}
